課程概述 Course Description
       本課程之主要目的在使學生瞭解國際貿易之基本原理及各類型貿易理論、國際貿易相關組織、貿易政策、區域經濟、以及國際投資等相關課題，本課程著重理論與實務並重。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    This course will be focused on the basic theory of international trade, various types of trading theories, organizations correspondent to international trade, trading policy, regional economies, and international investment issues.    

